1
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,879
=Ancient Love Poetry=

2
00:01:30,877 --> 00:01:33,000
=Episod 18=

3
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:35,350
Awak tak jaga rumah untuk dewa
dengan baik.

4
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:36,440
Mengapa datang ke sini?

5
00:01:37,070 --> 00:01:38,190
Betara mengadakan jamuan hari jadi,

6
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,440
Istana Qing Chi diajak.

7
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:40,710
Dewa tak ada di istana.

8
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,560
Selaku pengurus Istana Qing Chi,

9
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,110
sudah tentu saya perlu hadir
bagi pihak dewa.

10
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:45,310
Kenapa?

11
00:01:45,510 --> 00:01:47,070
Tuan rumah tak halau saya pun.

12
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:48,560
Selaku betara atasan Istana Syurga,

13
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,320
dapat pula awak berikan arahan
di Kediaman Da Ze.

14
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:52,510
Saya betara atasan
dari Istana Syurga, habis?

15
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:53,830
Dengar sini,

16
00:01:53,830 --> 00:01:55,720
Betara Dong Hua ialah betara atasan
dari Istana Syurga.

17
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,590
Istana Syurga bertanggungjawab terhadap
Kediaman Da Ze.

18
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,830
Itu tanggungjawab kami.

19
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,880
Awak menghina saya,

20
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,560
ertinya, menghina Istana Syurga!

21
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,800
Mengapa Istana Qing Chi

22
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,400
langsung tak hormati Istana Syurga?

23
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:07,560
Dua orang betara,

24
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,120
jangan marah.

25
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,350
Memandangkan Betari Feng Ran
mewakili Istana Qing Chi,

26
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:13,240
dia ialah tetamu penting.

27
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:16,120
Istana Syurga hantar putera ngah
dan puteri ke sini,

28
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:18,280
juga boleh nampak kamu pandang berat
terhadap Kediaman Da Ze.

29
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,830
Dalam hati Betara Dong Hua,

30
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,990
tiada sebarang perbezaan antara hadiah,

31
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:23,190
semuanya sama-sama bernilai.

32
00:02:23,670 --> 00:02:24,350
Cukup itu.

33
00:02:28,350 --> 00:02:29,280
Betara Zi Yuan,

34
00:02:29,950 --> 00:02:31,830
satu jamuan saja.

35
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:35,240
Biarpun awak tak sukanya,
awak perlu hormati dewa.

36
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:36,950
Puteri,

37
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,310
sebab,

38
00:02:39,230 --> 00:02:40,550
saya dapat siasat sesuatu
kebelakangan ini.

39
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,400
Saya sangat risau.

40
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:45,230
Padahal, perkara ini patut
dilaporkan kepada Raja Syurga,

41
00:02:45,230 --> 00:02:47,080
tapi memandangkan puteri
berada di sini hari ini,

42
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:49,200
saya minta puteri buat keputusan.

43
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,310
Betara Zi Yuan,

44
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,520
apa yang dapat awak siasat?

45
00:02:51,990 --> 00:02:52,840
Puteri,

46
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:55,520
beberapa hari lalu, saya dapati

47
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:57,520
di antara orang dalam Puak Betara,

48
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,760
terdapat orang yang
berkomplot dengan Puak Syaitan!

49
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,480
Siapa?

50
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,670
Awak maksudkan...

51
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,760
Saya maksudkan Feng Ran!

52
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:06,160
Puteri,

53
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:07,520
semua orang,

54
00:03:07,990 --> 00:03:09,200
orang ini berkomplot dengan
Puak Syaitan,

55
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:11,870
berniat untuk buat jahat
terhadap Puak Betara!

56
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:13,630
Pengawal,

57
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,120
tangkap Feng Ran.

58
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:15,950
Nanti dulu.

59
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:17,800
Puteri Jing Zhao,

60
00:03:18,270 --> 00:03:20,080
Istana Qing Chi terletak
di luar tiga alam,

61
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,200
bukan dalam bidang kuasa Istana Syurga.

62
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,520
Biarpun Raja Syurga nak
menyoal siasat saya,

63
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:26,480
dia perlu siasat hal sebenar.

64
00:03:26,990 --> 00:03:29,230
Awak cuba tangkap saya
tanpa tanya apa-apa pun,

65
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,270
terlalu tak munasabah ini.

66
00:03:32,350 --> 00:03:33,350
Semua orang tahu bahawa

67
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:36,120
Puak Syaitan dan Puak Betara tak dapat
bergaul dengan baik.

68
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:38,350
Memandangkan awak ada kesangsian
berkomplot dengan Puak Syaitan,

69
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,270
saya takkan berpeluh tubuh.

70
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:42,790
Sudah tentu perlu pertahankan
ketenteraman Puak Betara.

71
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,920
Ini alasan baik.

72
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,310
Saya datang dari Paya Yuan Ling,

73
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:50,070
tapi sejak bekerja di Istana Qing Chi,
saya tak berkaitan dengan Puak Syaitan!

74
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:51,430
Awak ada sebarang bukti

75
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,200
yang menunjukkan saya
berkomplot dengan Puak Syaitan?

76
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:54,430
Puteri,

77
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:55,790
semua orang,

78
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,560
beberapa hari lalu, anak murid saya

79
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,280
pergi uruskan sesuatu di Bukit Qi Lian,

80
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,790
tapi mereka tiba-tiba
dicederakan Puak Syaitan

81
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:04,280
yang muncul di Istana Qing Chi.

82
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,040
Puak Syaitan itu bukan saja
cederakan mereka berdua,

83
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:07,560
malah, juga merampas

84
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,840
hadiah yang saya sediakan
untuk Betara Dong Hua.

85
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,920
Karang api sepuluh ribu tahun!

86
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:12,870
Semua orang tahu bahawa

87
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:14,480
Dewa Gu Jun selalu mengembara di luar.

88
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:16,560
Dewi Hou Chi tak uruskan perkara.

89
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:18,280
Oleh itu, berpuluh-puluh ribu tahun ini,

90
00:04:18,670 --> 00:04:19,670
awak yang menguasai

91
00:04:19,670 --> 00:04:21,400
seluruh Istana Qing Chi.

92
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,840
Sekarang, Puak Syaitan muncul
di Istana Qing Chi.

93
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:24,760
Beritahu saya,

94
00:04:25,150 --> 00:04:27,150
siapa yang akan berkomplot dengan
Puak Syaitan selain daripada awak?

95
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,560
Karut!

96
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,040
Tiada Puak Syaitan di Istana Qing Chi!

97
00:04:30,430 --> 00:04:31,560
Tiada gunanya awak berdalih.

98
00:04:32,070 --> 00:04:32,590
Wu Wang!

99
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:34,510
Ya.

100
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,640
Tangannya dicederakan kuasa syaitan.

101
00:04:45,150 --> 00:04:46,430
Berdasarkan luka ini,

102
00:04:46,790 --> 00:04:48,310
bagaimana dapat buktikan
ia dicederakan kuasa syaitan?

103
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,560
Biarpun dicederakan kuasa syaitan,

104
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:51,840
bagaimana awak dapat buktikan
ini angkara Istana Qing Chi?

105
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:53,510
Bagaimana awak dapat buktikan
awak tak bersalah

106
00:04:53,710 --> 00:04:55,480
dengan katakan saya memfitnah awak?

107
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,360
(Jelasnya, hal ini tak benar,)

108
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,870
(tapi dia bertegas.)

109
00:04:59,230 --> 00:05:00,590
(Apakah dia cuba pergunakan hal ini
untuk timbulkan masalah?)

110
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,670
Feng Ran.

111
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:04,360
Memandangkan Istana Qing Chi terletak
di luar tiga alam,

112
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,760
awak tak patut campur tangan dalam
urusan betara dan syaitan.

113
00:05:07,230 --> 00:05:08,310
Bertahun-tahun ini, Dewa Bapa saya

114
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,200
melayan Istana Qing Chi dengan sopan.

115
00:05:11,150 --> 00:05:13,640
Awak tak patut
berkomplot dengan Puak Syaitan

116
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,840
dan buat sesuatu yang jahat
terhadap Puak Betara

117
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,560
apabila Dewa Gu Jun mengembara di luar.

118
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,400
Sopan?

119
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:20,560
Istana Qing Chi dan Istana Syurga
berkedudukan sama.

120
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:22,950
Kami tak perlukan kesopanan
daripada Istana Syurga.

121
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:24,510
Jing Zhao,

122
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:26,920
awak cuba buli Istana Qing Chi

123
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,150
kerana Dewa Gu Jun mengembara di luar.

124
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,790
Perbuatan awak

125
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:32,000
terlalu teruk.

126
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:32,840
Biadab!

127
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,360
Kalau awak nak tunjukkan gaya awak
sebagai puteri,

128
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,510
balik ke Istana Syurga.

129
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:36,590
Baik.

130
00:05:37,670 --> 00:05:38,230
Feng Ran,

131
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,400
awak tak nak mengaku, betul?

132
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:41,000
Saya tahu, awak takkan mengaku.

133
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,870
Tak apa.

134
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:43,590
Namun, saya beritahu awak dengan jujur,

135
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:45,310
saya telah buat mohor

136
00:05:45,710 --> 00:05:46,950
pada karang api sepuluh ribu tahun itu.

137
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,840
Kalau-kalau orang dari Istana Qing Chi

138
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:50,040
yang cederakan orang
dan rampas barang bernilai,

139
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,360
kita akan tahu selepas menguji.

140
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,390
Macam mana?

141
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,150
Feng Ran,

142
00:05:58,830 --> 00:06:00,110
apa lagi yang ingin awak cakap?

143
00:06:00,590 --> 00:06:01,360
Kebetulan pula.

144
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,150
Saya datang ke sini untuk
buat perhitungan dengan awak.

145
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:07,080
Anak murid awak ceroboh masuk ke Istana
Qing Chi dan curi mata air rohani.

146
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,830
Karang api ini ialah bukti.

147
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,150
Tak sangka

148
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:14,590
orang keji memutarbalikkan hakikat.

149
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:16,800
Betara Zi Yuan,

150
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:18,390
tangkap dia!

151
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:18,920
Ya,

152
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:19,680
puteri.

153
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,080
Saya nak tengok

154
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,310
kalau-kalau Betara Laut Utara
yang tak suka cari kawan

155
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,990
berani berlagak kelak.

156
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,360
Apa yang dia lakukan lagi?

157
00:07:29,550 --> 00:07:31,800
Jahat! Tak sangka dia mengikat saya
di dewan depan.

158
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,310
(Tak boleh.)

159
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:50,520
(Kuasa rohani saya rendah.)

160
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,960
(Kalau masuk begitu saja, saya akan
timbulkan masalah untuk Feng Ran.)

161
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,680
Kalau hadapi bahaya,

162
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:56,990
masukkan kuasa betara sendiri
ke dalam rantai tangan ini.

163
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:58,870
Ia dapat mempertingkatkan
tahap kuasa awak segera.

164
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,550
Masanya agak pendek,

165
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,240
tapi cukup untuk lepaskan diri
daripada bahaya.

166
00:08:05,416 --> 00:08:08,736
(Syurga dan Bumi Yang Luas Bentang)

167
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:09,990
Kipas Bulu Phoenix Permaisuri Syurga.

168
00:08:10,550 --> 00:08:11,110
Jing Zhao,

169
00:08:11,590 --> 00:08:12,680
awak keji.

170
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,800
Untuk menentang orang seperti awak,

171
00:08:13,990 --> 00:08:15,150
tak perlu kisah tentang akhlak.

172
00:08:15,590 --> 00:08:17,040
Dulu, demi seorang syaitan,

173
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,710
awak hampir menyebabkan
kematian abang saya.

174
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,360
Kini, awak berkomplot dengan Puak
Syaitan dan huru-harakan Alam Kayangan.

175
00:08:21,550 --> 00:08:22,680
Perbuatan awak tak boleh dimaafkan.

176
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,390
Betara Zi Yuan,

177
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,800
tangkap dia untuk saya.

178
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,640
Ya, puteri!

179
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:28,040
Puteri,

180
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:30,830
Betari Feng Ran tetap pengurus
Istana Qing Chi.

181
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,550
Biarpun dia berkomplot
dengan Puak Syaitan,

182
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:35,040
patut tanya dewa atasan
di Istana Qing Chi

183
00:08:35,040 --> 00:08:36,150
sebelum jatuhkan hukuman.

184
00:08:36,430 --> 00:08:39,310
Semua orang tahu, dah sepuluh ribu tahun
Dewa Gu Jun mengembara.

185
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:40,590
Hal ini berkaitan dengan Puak Syaitan,

186
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:43,200
patut Istana Syurga yang uruskannya.

187
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,710
Puteri,

188
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,640
ada lagi seorang dewa atasan
di Istana Qing Chi.

189
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:47,550
Xian Shan,

190
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,240
adakah awak maksudkan

191
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,920
dewi yang tak berguna
di Istana Qing Chi itu?

192
00:08:50,430 --> 00:08:52,110
Saya dengar bahawa dia tiada
kuasa betara bumi pun.

193
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:13,990
Kuatnya kuasa rohani ini.

194
00:09:16,110 --> 00:09:17,990
Mengapa saya macam pernah jumpa
kuasa rohani begini?

195
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,870
Orang lemah begini

196
00:09:19,990 --> 00:09:21,270
tak layak buat keputusan
untuk hal besar.

197
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:22,830
Jangan mengarut

198
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,480
dan menghina dewa atasan
Istana Qing Chi!

199
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:26,830
Awak hampir mati,
berani awak berlagak lagi.

200
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,080
Sudahlah.

201
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,270
Saya akan bunuh awak!

202
00:10:01,310 --> 00:10:02,480
(Mengapa dia berubah menjadi
orang yang berlainan?)

203
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:06,070
(Mengapa begini serupa dengan dewi
dalam mimpi saya?)

204
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:07,920
- Tuk guru.
- Tuk guru.

205
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:12,920
Siapa awak?

206
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,920
Berani awak ceroboh masuk
ke Kediaman Da Ze

207
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,560
dan cederakan betara Istana Syurga saya

208
00:10:17,070 --> 00:10:18,560
serta huru-harakan
jamuan hari jadi betara.

209
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:19,510
Ceroboh masuk?

210
00:10:20,070 --> 00:10:21,270
Betara Xian Shan, tengoklah.

211
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:23,560
Adakah

212
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,320
mahaguru yang tulis kad jemputan ini?

213
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,240
Saya datang kerana diajak.

214
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:28,880
Saya bukan ceroboh masuk.

215
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:31,480
Salam sejahtera, dewi.

216
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:32,880
Jing Zhao.

217
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,000
Awak cederakan pengurus
Istana Qing Chi saya.

218
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,920
Saya hanya cederakan
seorang betara atasan awak.

219
00:10:38,190 --> 00:10:39,190
Apa masalahnya?

220
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:41,040
Awak Hou Chi?

221
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:42,480
Mustahil.

222
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,800
Mustahil Hou Chi ada kuasa rohani
yang begini kuat.

223
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:48,560
Salam sejahtera, Dewi Hou Chi.

224
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:52,560
Salam sejahtera, Dewi Hou Chi.

225
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:55,560
Salam sejahtera, dewi.

226
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:57,320
Salam sejahtera, dewi atasan.

227
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:59,360
Tadi, awak kata
kuasa rohani saya rendah,

228
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,440
tak layak buat keputusan?

229
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,360
Tidak.

230
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:03,390
Tidak, dewi atasan.

231
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:04,480
Saya tak pernah cakap begitu.

232
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,750
Saya tak tahu tentang kedatangan awak.

233
00:11:07,190 --> 00:11:09,070
Sila berikan muka
kepada Istana Syurga...

234
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,240
Istana Syurga?

235
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:11,800
Tadi, awak kata,

236
00:11:12,070 --> 00:11:13,920
pengurus Istana Qing Chi
berkomplot dengan Puak Syaitan.

